Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.tui.input.setup

Class AskAddress

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.view.tui.input.Input
it.polimi.ingsw.view.tui.input.setup.AskAddress
public class AskAddress extends Input
The AskAddress class represents an input prompt for asking the user to insert a server address in order to create a connection to the server. It extends the Input class.
Author:
Tommaso Trabacchin, Melanie Tonarelli, Emanuele Valsecchi, Adem Shehi
